OL,3,CStockport Hat Works Museum officially
OL,4,Cre-opens to public
OL,6,FStockport's Hat Work Museum has
OL,7,Fofficially re-opened after being
OL,8,Fclosed for four years for
OL,9,Frefurbishment.
OL,11,FThe regeneration of the the Hat Work
OL,12,Fis part of Stockport Council's
OL,13,F#1billion transformation of the city's
OL,14,Ftown centre.
OL,16,FThe Hat Work Museum, which re-opened
OL,17,Fto the public on Thursday 21 March
OL,18,F2024, is the only museum dedicated to
OL,19,Fthe hatting industry, hats and
OL,20,Fheadwear in the UK.
