OL,3,CStockport Hat Works Museum officially
OL,4,Cre-opens to public
OL,6,FIt first opened its doors back in 2000
OL,7,Fand showcases an array of Stockport's
OL,8,Fhat collections in different colours,
OL,9,Fshapes, patterns and textures.
OL,11,FFollowing the renovation of
OL,12,FStockport's Hat Works, there are now
OL,13,Fmore than 1000 new objects which are
OL,14,Fon display to the public for the first
OL,15,Ftime.
OL,17,FMr Roberts added: "It's amazing. In
OL,18,Four hat museum, I could wear different
OL,19,Fhat here every day for three and half
OL,20,Fyears and I still wouldn't have got
OL,21,Fthrough the entire collection."
