OL,3,CStockport Hat Works Museum officially
OL,4,Cre-opens to public
OL,6,FThe machinery floor has also been
OL,7,Fextensively renovated with new
OL,8,Fdisplays and tours.
OL,10,FVisitors can also learn about
OL,11,FStockport's hat trade and view its
OL,12,Fdisplay of restored Victorian hat-
OL,13,Fmaking machines which are now in
OL,14,Fmotion for the first time since 2016.
OL,16,FStockport's industrial history was
OL,17,Fpredominantly hatting which boomed
OL,18,Fafter the 1800s and into the 1900s
OL,19,Fwith the the last hat factory closing
OL,20,Fin 1997.
